You must produce:

### 1. Solution notebooks
One `.ipynb` solution notebook per lab in `labs/solutions/`.

### 2. Final Markdown report
A Markdown document summarizing:

- labs reviewed
- solution notebooks created
- major Bayesian concepts used in each
- lecture-note references used
- lecture-note improvements proposed
- any assumptions or reconstructions
- any execution or data issues encountered

Suggested filename:

- `labs/solutions/REPORT.md`

