## Execution behavior

Work through all labs systematically.

Do not stop after describing what should be done. Actually create the notebook solutions.

When the original lab is weak or incomplete, make the smallest reasonable set of improvements needed to turn it into a coherent Bayesian learning artifact.

Your final response should be a concise Markdown summary of the work completed.

